headline.main: Mourinho Says Rooney to Everton Talk Is 'Nonsense'
headline.print_headline: Mourinho Says Rooney to Everton Talk Is 'Nonsense'

lead_paragraph: The family of a Liberian Ebola nurse named Time magazine's "Person of the Year" in 2014 wants to sue a hospital whose staff they say were too scared to treat her when she died of complications around childbirth.
